{
  "name": "MAM Service Quiz — save leads to data table",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 1. Before you activate\n\n**a) Create the data table** — name it exactly `MAM Quiz Leads`, with the columns listed in the note to the right. The Data table node below looks it up **by name**, so the name must match.\n\n**b) Create the reCAPTCHA credential** — Credentials → new **Query Auth**:\n- Name: `reCAPTCHA secret`\n- Parameter name: `secret`\n- Value: your reCAPTCHA v3 **SECRET** key\n\nThen open **Verify reCAPTCHA** and select it.\n\nThe secret lives in credentials, not in this workflow, so it stays out of any export.\n\n**c) Copy the Production URL** from the Webhook node into `assets/js/config.js` → `webhookUrl`.\n\n**d) Set Allowed Origins** on the Webhook node to your real domains. CORS is the usual failure point.",
        "height": 520,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "note-setup",
      "name": "Setup",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-660, -120]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2. Data table columns\n\nCreate `MAM Quiz Leads` with exactly these:\n\n| Column | Type |\n| --- | --- |\n| submitted_at | date |\n| status | string |\n| name | string |\n| email | string |\n| phone | string |\n| website | string |\n| profile | string |\n| business_type | string |\n| budget | string |\n| challenge | string |\n| primary_service | string |\n| primary_service_url | string |\n| supporting_services | string |\n| budget_tier | string |\n| all_ranked | string |\n| recaptcha_configured | boolean |\n| recaptcha_success | boolean |\n| recaptcha_score | number |\n| client_spam_score | number |\n| spam_signals | string |\n| seconds_to_complete | number |\n| page_url | string |\n| referrer | string |\n| user_agent | string |\n| utm_source | string |\n| utm_medium | string |\n| utm_campaign | string |\n| gclid | string |\n| fbclid | string |\n| client_ip | string |\n\nDo **not** add an `id` column — n8n generates row IDs itself.\n\nIf the insert complains about `submitted_at`, switch that column to `string`.",
        "height": 900,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "note-columns",
      "name": "Columns",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-220, -120]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 3. Every record is saved\n\nNothing is rejected. The row always lands in the table; `status` is either `new` or `review`.\n\n`review` when **any** of:\n- `client_spam_score >= 60`\n- reCAPTCHA is configured but verification failed\n- reCAPTCHA score < 0.5\n\nWhile `recaptchaSiteKey` is still empty in `config.js`, the payload reports `configured: false` and everything is marked `new` — so the quiz works before you finish the reCAPTCHA setup.\n\n### ⚠️ Harden this once your site key is live\n\nThat escape hatch reads `configured` **from the request**, so anyone POSTing straight to this webhook can omit it and land in `new`.\n\nOnce reCAPTCHA works, open **Build lead row** → `status` and replace the whole expression with:\n\n```\n{{ ($json.success === true && ($json.score ?? 0) >= 0.5 && ($('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.security?.client_spam_score ?? 0) < 60) ? 'new' : 'review' }}\n```\n\nNow nothing reaches `new` without a token Google actually verified.\n\nTune the 60 and the 0.5 once you have seen real traffic.",
        "height": 700,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "note-policy",
      "name": "Policy",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [640, -120]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 4. Your turn\n\nHang the rest of the automation off these two branches — Slack/email alert, CRM push, the confirmation email promised on the form (\"We send a copy, plus a short competitor snapshot, to your inbox\").\n\nThe visitor already has their results by this point, so nothing here is on the critical path.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "note-extend",
      "name": "Extend",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1720, -120]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "mam-service-quiz",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "allowedOrigins": "https://moveaheadmedia.github.io,https://www.moveaheadmedia.co.th",
          "ignoreBots": true
        }
      },
      "id": "quiz-webhook",
      "name": "Quiz Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [-180, 860],
      "webhookId": "a7f3c1d2-9b48-4e06-8f51-2c9d6e4b7a30"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api/siteverify",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpQueryAuth",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "specifyQuery": "keypair",
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "response",
              "value": "={{ $json.body?.security?.recaptcha?.token ?? '' }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "remoteip",
              "value": "={{ ($json.headers?.['x-forwarded-for'] ?? '').split(',')[0].trim() }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "timeout": 8000,
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "neverError": true,
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "verify-recaptcha",
      "name": "Verify reCAPTCHA",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.4,
      "position": [60, 860],
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput",
      "notesInFlow": true,
      "notes": "Fails soft — a broken CAPTCHA must never lose a lead"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "manual",
        "includeOtherFields": false,
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            { "id": "f-submitted-at", "name": "submitted_at", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.submitted_at ?? $now.toISO() }}" },

            { "id": "f-status", "name": "status", "type": "string", "value": "={{ ($('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.security?.client_spam_score ?? 0) >= 60 ? 'review' : ($('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.security?.recaptcha?.configured !== true ? 'new' : (($json.success === true && ($json.score ?? 0) >= 0.5) ? 'new' : 'review')) }}" },

            { "id": "f-name", "name": "name", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.lead?.name ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-email", "name": "email", "type": "string", "value": "={{ ($('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.lead?.email ?? '').toLowerCase().trim() }}" },
            { "id": "f-phone", "name": "phone", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.lead?.phone ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-website", "name": "website", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.lead?.website ?? '' }}" },

            { "id": "f-profile", "name": "profile", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.answers?.profile?.label ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-type", "name": "business_type", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.answers?.type?.label ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-budget", "name": "budget", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.answers?.budget?.label ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-challenge", "name": "challenge", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.answers?.challenge?.label ?? '' }}" },

            { "id": "f-primary", "name": "primary_service", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.recommendation?.primary?.name ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-primary-url", "name": "primary_service_url", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.recommendation?.primary?.url ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-supporting", "name": "supporting_services", "type": "string", "value": "={{ ($('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.recommendation?.supporting ?? []).map(s => s.name).join(', ') }}" },
            { "id": "f-tier", "name": "budget_tier", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.recommendation?.budget_tier ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-ranked", "name": "all_ranked", "type": "string", "value": "={{ JSON.stringify($('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.recommendation?.all_ranked ?? []) }}" },

            { "id": "f-rc-configured", "name": "recaptcha_configured", "type": "boolean", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.security?.recaptcha?.configured === true }}" },
            { "id": "f-rc-success", "name": "recaptcha_success", "type": "boolean", "value": "={{ $json.success === true }}" },
            { "id": "f-rc-score", "name": "recaptcha_score", "type": "number", "value": "={{ $json.score ?? 0 }}" },
            { "id": "f-spam-score", "name": "client_spam_score", "type": "number", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.security?.client_spam_score ?? 0 }}" },
            { "id": "f-spam-signals", "name": "spam_signals", "type": "string", "value": "={{ JSON.stringify($('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.security?.signals ?? {}) }}" },

            { "id": "f-seconds", "name": "seconds_to_complete", "type": "number", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.seconds_to_complete ?? 0 }}" },
            { "id": "f-page", "name": "page_url", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.page_url ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-referrer", "name": "referrer", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.referrer ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-ua", "name": "user_agent", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.user_agent ?? '' }}" },

            { "id": "f-utm-source", "name": "utm_source", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.tracking?.utm_source ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-utm-medium", "name": "utm_medium", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.tracking?.utm_medium ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-utm-campaign", "name": "utm_campaign", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.tracking?.utm_campaign ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-gclid", "name": "gclid", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.tracking?.gclid ?? '' }}" },
            { "id": "f-fbclid", "name": "fbclid", "type": "string", "value": "={{ $('Quiz Webhook').item.json.body?.meta?.tracking?.fbclid ?? '' }}" },

            { "id": "f-ip", "name": "client_ip", "type": "string", "value": "={{ ($('Quiz Webhook').item.json.headers?.['x-forwarded-for'] ?? '').split(',')[0].trim() }}" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "ignoreConversionErrors": true,
          "dotNotation": false
        }
      },
      "id": "build-lead-row",
      "name": "Build lead row",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [300, 860]
    },
    {
